data.description: Spacious 2 bed 1.1 bath home in Baker City.  1364 sf(m/l) on the main level. Features include hardwood floors, F/A heat and a small garage. Full partially finished basement has lots of potential.  Home sits on a large .87 acre lot.  Includes numerous fruit trees and gorgeous views of the Elkhorn Mountains!
